---
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout
  title="Getting Help"
  description="Where to get help and report issues."
  prevPage={{ slug: "benchmark-issues", title: "Benchmark Issues" }}
  nextPage={{ slug: "contributing", title: "Contributing" }}
>
  <h2>Community Support</h2>
  <p>The fastest way to get help is through our community:</p>

  <h3>Discord Server</h3>
  <p>
    Join our <a
      href="https://discord.gg/SFsf4GQhJU"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer">Discord server</a
    >
    for quick help from the community and developers.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Ask questions in the support channels</li>
    <li>Share your feedback and suggestions</li>
    <li>Connect with other users</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Bug Reports</h2>
  <p>Found a bug? Report it on GitHub:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>
      Go to <a
        href="https://github.com/ARm8-2/refleks/issues"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Issues</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>Click "New Issue"</li>
    <li>
      Describe the problem: what you were doing, what you expected, and what
      actually happened
    </li>
    <li>Include any error messages or screenshots if possible</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Feature Requests</h2>
  <p>Have an idea for a new feature? We'd love to hear it:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>
      Go to <a
        href="https://github.com/ARm8-2/refleks/issues"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Issues</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>Click "New Issue"</li>
    <li>Describe your idea and why it would be useful</li>
  </ol>

  <div class="note">
    <strong>Tip:</strong> Before reporting a bug, check the <a
      href="/docs/runs-not-appearing">troubleshooting guides</a
    >
    - your issue might already have a solution!
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
